<subSubSection id="B4A865738700C66A04F8FC0CFC71DC84" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="FC0D36F88700C66A04F8FC0CFC71DC84" blockId="20.[151,1437,933,1930]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">
<emphasis id="CEC6EAEA8700C66A04F8FC0CFEADDCDF" bold="true" box="[151,284,933,959]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Etymology</emphasis>
. We are pleased to name this genus in memory of the late Frank T. Hovore for his friendship and many contributions to the study of 
<taxonomicName id="3BB24D7B8700C66A065EFC63FD6FDC84" box="[561,734,970,996]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Cerambycidae</taxonomicName>
. Masculine gender.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
